Reference-contexts: To evaluate the event data further on every mirror system an additional controller like a DSP or neural device, for example the SAND/1-ASIC (simply application neural 2 device) <ref> [5] </ref>, is integrated. We show the first-level and the second-level trigger more detailed in the next section. Based on this structure a third-level trigger is possible working on the local eye-memory. The three eyes support the data management for storing the events and the intelligence for data exchange.
